title: Start
body:
This is the start of the Kent Route.
-> Keep going.
    <<statDown Friendship J-Pe>>
    <<statDown Friendship J-Pe>>
    <<statDown Freindship J-Pe>>
    <<statDown Friendship Lee>>
    <<statDown Friendship Lee>>
    <<statDown Freindship Lee>>
    Stats up.
-> Don't
    <<statUp Friendship J-Pe>>
    <<statUp Friendship J-Pe>>
    <<statUp Freindship J-Pe>>
    <<statUp Friendship Lee>>
    <<statUp Friendship Lee>>
    <<statUp Freindship Lee>>
    Stats down.
